The '''''Firefly''-class transport''' was a ship seen on the planet [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] airways shortly after the declaration of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].<ref name="Prey">''[[Evasive Action: Prey]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The ship can be seen in the sixth strip of ''[[Evasive Action: Prey]]''.<ref name="Prey" /> Illustrator [[Tom Hodges]] included it as a reference to the titular vessel of the TV series [[Wikipedia:Firefly (TV series)|''Firefly'']] and film [[Wikipedia:Serenity (film)|''Serenity'']].<ref name="JCF">{{JCFCite|url=posts/23417486|board=Literature|thread=Daily Hyperspace SW Comic Strip Adventures Discussion-"Rookies" & "Evasive Action: End Game"|user=[[Tom Hodges|TDHArtist]]|PTtime= 3/14/2006|time=9:29 PM|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328171835/https://boards.theforce.net/threads/daily-hyperspace-sw-comic-strip-adventures-discussion-rookies-evasive-action-end-game.16431027/page-27}}</ref>

